{"tid":1012922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 屯門千鳥翱翔 　街坊讚好意頭","createTime":"2019-02-08T03:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T18:48:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fc7720c67f487c5201c3fc76ca1812cf5cfab900","tid":1012922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190208/20608567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190208%2F20608567&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=b9818ae1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190208%2F20608567&h=25942c80\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190208/20608567</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月08日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n屯門千鳥翱翔 　街坊讚好意頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190208/large/08ls4p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F08ls4p04.jpg&h=2f0d2a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大年初二早上8時許，屯門上空出現千鳥翱翔的壯觀景色（圖），巿民用手機拍短片之餘，頻呼「好得意」、「有福氣」。屯門女街坊見到至少三大群候鳥在青松仙苑附近天空向南飛，部份以V字形陣式飛行，她對於提早見到這麼多候鳥，感覺很幸運，但同時亦疑惑候鳥提早出現是否與全球暖化有關。<br />\n<br />\n生態教育及資源中心總監程詩灝估計片段中的候鳥是鸕鶿，約半個月前亦曾有市民在青馬大橋深井對出海面，見過數以千計的鸕鶿飛翔。雖然程認為屯門上空出現大量鸕鶿未必與全球暖化有關，但他指「香港市民越來越關注身邊嘅生態變化，對全球暖化嘅關注度提高咗」，實屬好事。鸕鶿每年隨着冬北季候風大舉抵港過冬，總數可達一萬多隻，至2月左右又會隨氣流飛返北方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片<br />\n#MeToo個個都要爆，但係唔一定要舉牌！只要你肯爆，無論好事、壞事、憤怒事，正嘢、衰嘢、古怪嘢，影低佢，《蘋果》幫你爆，更設爆相爆片大獎賞，除咗爆相畀$500、爆片送$1,000嘅基本獎賞外，仲會選出每周之星，每星期最高單日總點擊頭5名即刻科水$10,000，而每月15號至翌月14號期間獲得全月最高單日總點擊者，更可以成為每月盟主，額外獎賞$100,000，係$100,000！爆相爆片必須為本報獨家採用，一經刊登立即有獎！<br />\n爆相爆片WhatsApp：6383 6568<br />\n<br />\n參加細則<br />\n1.爆相爆片必須由參加者拍攝。<br />\n2.若本報發現任何造假情況，將取消其參賽資格。<br />\n3.壹傳媒集團員工及親屬不可參加。<br />\n4.本報會保留採用爆相爆片與否和獎項分配的一切權利，如有任何爭議，以本報決定為準。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n黃牛黨猖獗　警放蛇掃蕩"},{"pid":"bf8325641c0a966778eb5effa2519def474b9ab9","tid":1012922,"uid":57844,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"雀仔飛都可以係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7d97145007fff8005f158c647136f77defce47","tid":1012922,"uid":146092,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"地震先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcee9c30807ac2c8954df041ba7ce3e22735c95f","tid":1012922,"uid":3515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:19:10.000Z","msg":"支那工廠收晒工空氣好咪多雀囉"},{"pid":"29906e8958780f73edffcb6df335379b857a5278","tid":1012922,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:15:43.000Z","msg":"年中見唔少次呢啲雀鳥遷徙"},{"pid":"a0479752cb9bbd67c8389d58b977190a281f1ac3","tid":1012922,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:17:51.000Z","msg":"鳥走難真係好兆頭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422f3a1d4c648c0e73d780c575546648cfa6b4fd","tid":1012922,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"2012<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45ca0a7373e6e902dbce4810ca03a118b65b4be","tid":1012922,"uid":25794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"走緊佬喎大佬<br />\n好意頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d0a2c6916a6e7c8839ff789625917fe73a45fb","tid":1012922,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:33:15.000Z","msg":"屯門實死好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0cb6653ab710768b6f2f49f61518ff73e31a6a","tid":1012922,"uid":13897,"like":1,"dislik